data.description: What a dream of a home!  Sprawl out on over 1 acre of land and gorgeous property ready for you to make it home!  There's so much space to breathe!  Entertain family and guests in the super large kitchen that opens to a massive dining room and living room.  Main bedroom has large en-suite bathroom equipped with large soaking tub.  So many windows throughout makes plenty of natural light coming through the home.  Fully finished basement with 2nd kitchen.  Large 3 car garage. Bring your decorating ideas as this is the place to make home.
